o%2F1%2F177%2F008J678FD548540BF73641px.jpg&h=9672cb5f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d70fa4d7c15fb39d99a31d7200686e490272ad3","tid":240524,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起之前有單咩發現切錯 <br />\n之後醫生怕係另一面 切埋黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f31f9d6f3c667df0830c1b21ef5f7e936a29dc","tid":240524,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"醫學既野邊有100%<br />\n你估一照超聲波，畫面會有個箭咀指住這是癌咩?<br />\n<br />\n你話食下抗生素睇下會唔會消腫，一陣遲左處理擴散左又話你遲左治療<br />\n<br />\n所有治療都要比較好處同壞處<br />\n睪丸有2粒，切左1粒都仲生到仔<br />\n命就得1條，擴散左就玩完<br />\n<br />\n結果論去睇，個個都中晒六合彩啦"},{"pid":"8041eb72b5ece03551818019702b9fd971afc8f9","tid":240524,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20090323/12525232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20090323%2F12525232&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9f5d694f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20090323%2F12525232&h=7b57789d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20090323/12525232</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2009年</span></span></blockquote><br />\n又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重大事件就可不了了之？"},{"pid":"41611dee64da375a8343b7e9f8bfc3224dfe98ac","tid":240524,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:48:59.000Z","msg":"殘忍的單丸非你專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1de1a3f61ef7514bcb26e88058bfb70145f0661","tid":240524,"uid":116211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"e神陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}